长时间记忆、实时交互</span><span class="inline whitespace-pre-wrap md:hidden">多模态与上下文环境感知
长时间记忆、实时交互</span></div><div class="desc mx-auto mt-[24px] w-full max-w-[880px] whitespace-pre-wrap px-[24px] text-center text-[13px] font-normal leading-[22px] text-[#888] md:max-w-[1164px] md:text-[16px] md:leading-[30px] md:text-[#5D5D5D]"><span class="hidden whitespace-pre-wrap md:inline">我们自主研发了国内首个情绪赋能多模态大语言模型Soul X，其具备长时间记忆、上下文与环境感知功能，凭借多模态感知与实时交互能力，能够识别、理解并动态响应用户的情绪，为用户提供创作灵感和互动支持。</span><span class="inline whitespace-pre-wrap md:hidden">我们自主研发了国内首个情绪赋能多模态大语言模型Soul X，其具备长时间记忆、上下文与环境感知功能，凭借多模态感知与实时交互能力，能够识别、理解并动态响应用户的情绪，为用户提供创作灵感和互动支持。</span></div><div class="wave-container screen-fourth-wave relative mt-[144px] hidden h-[300px] w-full md:block"><video class="absolute inset-0 block h-full w-full object-cover text-[0] focus:outline-none focus:ring-0" autoPlay="" loop="" muted="" playsInline=""><source src="https://china-img.soulapp.cn/admin/2026-01-16/e8cf5a1a-5d9f-40b8-9a88-38a211ede196.mp4" type="video/mp4"/></video><div class="wave-content absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 z-10 flex h-auto w-[203px] -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 flex-col items-center"><img alt="soulx" loading="lazy" width="199" height="50" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-soulx.99acb66d.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-soulx.99acb66d.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-soulx.99acb66d.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75"/><div class="wave-desc absolute text-center text-[28px] font-[600] text-s02 opacity-0 bottom-[109px]">原生情绪价值第一大模型</div></div></div><img alt="soulx" loading="lazy" width="750" height="166" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="wave-container relative mt-[92px] block w-full md:hidden" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fimg-screen-4-mb.f9515de9.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fimg-screen-4-mb.f9515de9.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fimg-screen-4-mb.f9515de9.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75"/></section><section class="time-line relative flex w-full flex-col items-center"><div class="title pt-[100px] text-center text-[24px] font-extrabold text-s02 md:pt-[120px] md:text-[38px]"><span class="hidden whitespace-pre-wrap md:inline">模应一体：让用户自发玩起来</span><span class="inline whitespace-pre-wrap md:hidden">模应一体：
让用户自发玩起来</span></div><div class="desc mx-auto mt-[12px] max-w-[880px] px-[24px] text-center text-[13px] font-normal leading-[22px] text-[#888] md:mt-[24px] md:max-w-[1164px] md:text-[16px] md:leading-[30px] md:text-[#5D5D5D]"><span class="hidden whitespace-pre-wrap md:inline">Soul 同步探索大模型开发与应用落地，让用户自发&quot;玩&quot;起来。在Soul，大模型开发并非是最终目的，而是为社交核心场景寻找提升用户体验的创新解决方案。为此，Soul在场景中洞察需求，通过自研模型推出创新应用，在社交场景中快速触达用户获得反馈、实现迭代。</span><span class="inline whitespace-pre-wrap md:hidden">Soul 同步探索大模型开发与应用落地，让用户自发&quot;玩&quot;起来。在Soul，大模型开发并非是最终目的，而是为社交核心场景寻找提升用户体验的创新解决方案。为此，Soul在场景中洞察需求，通过自研模型推出创新应用，在社交场景中快速触达用户获得反馈、实现迭代。</span></div><div class="imgs relative mx-auto hidden w-[1000px] md:block md:h-[550px]"><img class="absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2" src="https://china-img.soulapp.cn/admin/2026-01-29/f24e2108-2e8f-4011-9d55-419765046e8c.png" alt="img-0" width="315.2" height="80"/><img class="absolute left-[200px] top-[20%]" src="https://china-img.soulapp.cn/admin/2026-01-22/8aba72f9-329a-481f-8565-59b708e794d9.png" alt="img-1" width="140.8" height="72"/><img class="absolute left-[50px] top-[40%]" src="https://china-img.soulapp.cn/admin/2026-01-22/ecd9df38-7934-4ca8-8f4f-4e43687e3713.png" alt="img-2" width="140.8" height="72"/><img class="absolute left-[160px] top-[65%]" src="https://china-img.soulapp.cn/admin/2026-01-22/971491d6-53e7-4489-b497-d03831bd31c0.png" alt="img-3" width="140.8" height="72"/><img class="absolute right-[250px] top-[13%]" src="https://china-img.soulapp.cn/admin/2026-01-22/229bf066-ad06-4243-b0dc-39065ae4b2d4.png" alt="img-4" width="80" height="120.8"/><img class="absolute right-[20px] top-[30%]" src="https://china-img.soulapp.cn/admin/2026-01-22/b5584465-d9d4-4f9b-a257-03332684e4d0.png" alt="img-5" width="128" height="160"/><img class="absolute right-[180px] top-[60%]" src="https://china-img.soulapp.cn/admin/2026-01-22/7594bd1a-af5f-4070-a987-36298947013c.png" alt="img-6" width="128" height="160"/></div><img alt="img-intro-mb" loading="lazy" width="750" height="700" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="mt-[44px] block w-full md:hidden" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fimg-screen-5-mb.10419a01.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fimg-screen-5-mb.10419a01.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Fimg-screen-5-mb.10419a01.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75"/></section><section class="milestone relative hidden h-screen w-full overflow-hidden md:block"><div class="milestone-title whitespace-pre-wrap pt-[120px] text-center text-[38px] font-extrabold text-s02">Soul的发展历程</div><div class="milestone-content relative mx-auto mt-[40px] block max-w-[1520px] px-[40px]"><div class="milestone-track relative z-[2] flex h-[420px] items-start will-change-transform"><svg class="timeline-curve relative" viewBox="0 0 1200 420" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMin meet" style="width:1200px;height:420px"><path id="timelinePath" d="M 0 70 C 450 70, 450 370, 900 370 S 1350 70, 1800 70" fill="none" stroke="#25D4D0" stroke-width="3" opacity="0.4" stroke-dasharray="3600" stroke-dashoffset="3492"></path></svg><div class="milestone-item relative z-[3] w-[220px] shrink-0 mr-[130px] above"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75"/><span class="date mt-[8px] text-[20px] font-semibold text-s02">2026年</span><p class="mt-[4px] text-[13px] font-[300] text-[#65687A] md:text-[14px]">先后开源实时数字人生成模型SoulX-FlashTalk（14B）、歌声合成模型 SoulX-Singer、实时数字人生成模型SoulX-FlashHead（1.3B），将多项能力推进到可规模商用阶段。</p></div><div class="milestone-item relative z-[3] w-[220px] shrink-0 mr-[130px] below"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75"/><span class="date mt-[8px] text-[20px] font-semibold text-s02">2025年</span><p class="mt-[4px] text-[13px] font-[300] text-[#65687A] md:text-[14px]">我们引入“情价比消费”概念，“原生情绪价值第一大模型”Soul X能力持续提升，拓展“情绪绿洲”价值。</p></div><div class="milestone-item relative z-[3] w-[220px] shrink-0 mr-[130px] above"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75"/><span class="date mt-[8px] text-[20px] font-semibold text-s02">2024年</span><p class="mt-[4px] text-[13px] font-[300] text-[#65687A] md:text-[14px]">我们确立“模应一体”的发展战略，同步探索大模型开发与平台内多元场景应用落地。</p></div><div class="milestone-item relative z-[3] w-[220px] shrink-0 mr-[130px] below"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75"/><span class="date mt-[8px] text-[20px] font-semibold text-s02">2023年</span><p class="mt-[4px] text-[13px] font-[300] text-[#65687A] md:text-[14px]">我们推出自研“原生情绪价值第一大模型”Soul X，入选《2023胡润全球独角兽榜》。</p></div><div class="milestone-item relative z-[3] w-[220px] shrink-0 mr-[130px] above"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75"/><span class="date mt-[8px] text-[20px] font-semibold text-s02">2022年</span><p class="mt-[4px] text-[13px] font-[300] text-[#65687A] md:text-[14px]">我们在移动应用程序中引入音乐房间功能（包括K歌房间及一起听歌），并正式推出Nawa引擎。</p></div><div class="milestone-item relative z-[3] w-[220px] shrink-0 mr-[130px] below"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75"/><span class="date mt-[8px] text-[20px] font-semibold text-s02">2021年</span><p class="mt-[4px] text-[13px] font-[300] text-[#65687A] md:text-[14px]">我们引入3D Avatar，日活跃用户数超过1千万人。</p></div><div class="milestone-item relative z-[3] w-[220px] shrink-0 mr-[130px] above"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75"/><span class="date mt-[8px] text-[20px] font-semibold text-s02">2020年</span><p class="mt-[4px] text-[13px] font-[300] text-[#65687A] md:text-[14px]">我们开始通过广告服务获利，并在移动应用程序中引入派对房间功能。</p></div><div class="milestone-item relative z-[3] w-[220px] shrink-0 mr-[130px] below"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75"/><span class="date mt-[8px] text-[20px] font-semibold text-s02">2019年</span><p class="mt-[4px] text-[13px] font-[300] text-[#65687A] md:text-[14px]">我们开始商业化。</p></div><div class="milestone-item relative z-[3] w-[220px] shrink-0 mr-[130px] above"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75"/><span class="date mt-[8px] text-[20px] font-semibold text-s02">2018年</span><p class="mt-[4px] text-[13px] font-[300] text-[#65687A] md:text-[14px]">Soul的日活跃用户数超过1百万人。</p></div><div class="milestone-item relative z-[3] w-[220px] shrink-0 mr-[130px] below"><img alt="star" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2F_next%2Fstatic%2Fmedia%2Ficon-star.78fa110c.png&amp;w=48&amp;q=75"/><span class="date mt-[8px] text-[20px] font-semibold text-s02">2017年</span><p class="mt-[4px] text-[13px] font-[300] text-[#65687A] md:text-[14px]">我们开发移动应用程序中的“星球”功能，并实施我们专有的推荐算法及先进的兴趣图谱描绘系统，使数据分析成为我们平台背后的驱动力。</p></div><div class="milestone-item relat